hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: Hold the line, please kamagrashop.pl opinie Just before serving, crumble the cheese (use a coarse grater if you prefer). Halve the avocados and lightly tap a knife blade into the stones. Remove by twisting and lifting. To peel, run a spoon between the flesh and the skin to lift it out. Cut into cubes and lightly sprinkle with the juice of the remaining lime. Place three pepper halves on a plate, fill each with the sweetcorn mixture, sprinkle with cheese and garnish with chopped avocado and coriander.
